nodes.text: A Triffian was among the defenders of the town of Deadend on the planet Kiffex when the Jedi Quinlan Vos and Tholme stormed the settlement. The Triffian tried to fight off the Jedi with a blaster, but the Jedi Knight and Jedi Master managed to overcome the Triffian and the other defenders. Nevertheless, the Triffian survived the encounter.
